<p>Unlike the rest of the home, which features pale grey walls, the sunroom is given an added sense of brightness due its unique white wood panel walls and ceiling.</p>

<p>Like the living room, the sunroom also happens to have a fireplace, which gives the room a more rustic feel.</p>

